# Day 01 â€“ Linear Regression

## Definition
Linear Regression is a supervised learning algorithm used to
predict a continuous dependent variable based on input features.
It provides a best fit line between the one independent variable and dependent variable.

## Formula
y = mx + c
where m=slope, c=intercept

## Use Cases
- Salary prediction
- House price prediction
- Sales forecasting

## Libraries Used
- Pandas
- NumPy
- scikit-learn
Donw it with both sklearn and with mathematical part.
